data.description: Looking for a fantastic home on a corner lot in Lone Star Trails? This home has it all! 3 bedrooms, 2 bath with an open concept kitchen to dining and living area!! Granite throughout! LARGE Seq primary suite! Primary bath has dual sinks, sep shower and tub with a HUGE closet that opens to the laundry! Gas fireplace in the living with TALL ceilings and a great sized kitchen bar perfect for gatherings! The back yard is a good size with ability to make larger on the corner lot! Don't miss this one!
